{"tid":1351811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英文文宣出爐！】(不斷更新）將721真相帶到法國街頭","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:47:14.000Z","uid":14259,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6ffa543ae4f97366673d86d4c888d5dbf98a6067","tid":1351811,"uid":14259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red721][/red]</span>黑警連開36發子彈，又喺元朗勾結黑幫打壓自由聲音，實在令好多人憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈譴責警方暴行，既然香港政府唔去處理，就唯有推向國際俾國外人士知道，等佢哋知道香港政府有幾無賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足啱啱極速製作好721的片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家幫推，同share出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rWJ7O3vPIWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrWJ7O3vPIWc&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn23s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=fd769d34\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rWJ7O3vPIWc</a><br />\n<br />\n身處法國的手足開始播片！！如有法國嘅巴絲，而又知道呢度喺邊嘅，過嚟支持吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TrM1rm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TrM1rm.png&h=6c8f9d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K14nzN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK14nzN9.png&h=847971a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xyojfp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xyojfp.png&h=c12e9271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家法國大節，所以有好多外國人喺度，<span style=\"color: red;\">不能只有香港人知道！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[size=4]]<span style=\"color: green;\">Save HONG KONG! NO China Extradition!</span>[/size=4<br />\n<br />\nHONG KONG people have been protesting for months.<br />\nWe request the Hong Kong government to withdraw Bill of China Extradition!<br />\nWe insist on preserving the rule of law in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nStudents protest with no weapons but only umbrellas.<br />\nStudents were shot by full gear police. SHAME ON HK POLICE!<br />\n<br />\nHundreds of citizens, including protesters, got attacked by Gangsters during their return trip on train.<br />\nThe GANGSTERS attacked with iron branch on whatever target, the pregnant, the elderly, the innocent. BUT HK Police just turned away from the citizens&rsquo; cry for help! <br />\n <br />\nTear gas didn't bring us down.<br />\nWE STAND FIRM!<br />\nBUT WE NEED YOUR HELP! WE NEED YOUR CONCERN AND SUPPORT!<br />\nPlease share these messages with your friends, Let the world see us. Let the world know what is happening in HONG KONG.<br />\nSee how EVIL is CHINA!<br />\n<br />\n因為趕住出片，稍後時間會再翻譯法文版作街頭廣播，將會不斷更新消息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5731f9f89d51a5fcbbabd526884a8e59dd51e8e2","tid":1351811,"uid":236471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b542438ce63913f72eb314ab5a09b4702e608291","tid":1351811,"uid":14259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"推到班黑警跪地認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d960fd7e3e5ccc07a0fd319cd8675bbc6bac70","tid":1351811,"uid":14259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"警黑合作可恥"},{"pid":"2fadadf51f8dbf27f2197f157d927e81238a6d9b","tid":1351811,"uid":14259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記噚晚中環同元朗嘅兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=